headline: Synopsys Week In Review: China Headwinds, NVIDIA Partnership, and Margin Expansion
summary: Synopsys (NASDAQ:SNPS) is having a week worth watching. The chip design software leader posted a 2.39% gain over the past five trading days, climbing from $426.88 to $437.09. Year to date, Synopsys is down 6.95%, and over the past month, shares have dropped 13.51%. That sounds like poor performance, but Synopsys is performing much better than ...
